{
  "dashboard": {
    "id": null,
    "uid": "wilsy-circuit-breaker",
    "title": "🏛️ WILSY OS - Sovereign Circuit Breaker HUD",
    "timezone": "browser",
    "refresh": "5s",
    "theme": "dark",
    "schemaVersion": 36,
    "version": 2,
    "panels": [
      {
        "type": "stat",
        "title": "Database Nucleus Link State",
        "id": 1,
        "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "w": 12, "h": 6 },
        "targets": [
          { "expr": "wilsy_breaker_state{tenantId=\"GLOBAL_ROOT\", component=\"DATABASE\"}", "legendFormat": "State" }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "mappings": [
              { "type": "value", "options": {
                "0": { "text": "CLOSED (OPERATIONAL)", "color": "green" },
                "1": { "text": "OPEN (FAILOVER ACTIVE)", "color": "red" },
                "2": { "text": "HALF-OPEN (RECOVERING)", "color": "yellow" }
              }}
            ],
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                { "color": "green", "value": 0 },
                { "color": "yellow", "value": 1 },
                { "color": "red", "value": 2 }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        "options": { "colorMode": "background", "justifyMode": "center" }
      },
      {
        "type": "stat",
        "title": "API Gateway Sovereign Circuit",
        "id": 2,
        "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 0, "w": 12, "h": 6 },
        "targets": [
          { "expr": "wilsy_breaker_state{tenantId=\"GLOBAL_ROOT\", component=\"API_GATEWAY\"}", "legendFormat": "State" }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "mappings": [
              { "type": "value", "options": {
                "0": { "text": "CLOSED (OPERATIONAL)", "color": "green" },
                "1": { "text": "OPEN (FAILOVER ACTIVE)", "color": "red" },
                "2": { "text": "HALF-OPEN (RECOVERING)", "color": "yellow" }
              }}
            ],
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                { "color": "green", "value": 0 },
                { "color": "yellow", "value": 1 },
                { "color": "red", "value": 2 }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        "options": { "colorMode": "background", "justifyMode": "center" }
      },
      {
        "type": "timeseries",
        "title": "Institutional Failover History (Strikes)",
        "id": 3,
        "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 6, "w": 24, "h": 8 },
        "targets": [
          { "expr": "increase(wilsy_counter_failover_events_total{tenantId=\"GLOBAL_ROOT\"}[1h])", "legendFormat": "{{component}} Failovers" }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "short",
            "custom": { "drawStyle": "bars" },
            "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "timeseries",
        "title": "Breaker Execution Latency (ms)",
        "id": 5,
        "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 14, "w": 12, "h": 6 },
        "targets": [
          { "expr": "wilsy_latency_request_latency{tenantId=\"GLOBAL_ROOT\", metric=\"breaker_response\"}", "legendFormat": "{{component}}" }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "ms",
            "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "timeseries",
        "title": "Telemetry Broadcast Velocity",
        "id": 6,
        "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 14, "w": 12, "h": 6 },
        "targets": [
          { "expr": "increase(wilsy_counter_telemetry_events_total{tenantId=\"GLOBAL_ROOT\"}[5m])", "legendFormat": "{{eventType}}" }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "short",
            "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "title": "Circuit Breaker Narrative Overlay",
        "id": 4,
        "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 20, "w": 24, "h": 4 },
        "options": {
          "mode": "markdown",
          "content": "### 🏛️ Sovereign Resilience Report\nThis HUD visualizes the **Failover State** of the Wilsy OS Core. A **CLOSED** state indicates total institutional stability. An **OPEN** state triggers the automated re‑anchoring protocol, isolating the fracture from the billion‑dollar ledger while the system executes a recovery sequence.\n\n_Audit Ref: ${__dashboard.name} | Refresh: ${__interval} | Tenant: GLOBAL_ROOT_"
        }
      }
    ]
  }
}
